# GitHub Personal Access Token
#
# Option A: Fine-grained PAT (Recommended for security)
# Scopes: Contents (Read/Write), Workflows (Read/Write), Profile (Read-only)
# Resource Owner: Must include all organizations you want to track.
#
# Option B: Classic PAT (Recommended for ease of use)
# Scopes: 'repo', 'workflow', 'read:user'
#
GH_TOKEN=your_token_here
